NAME
    Device::Hue - Perl module for the Philips Hue light system

VERSION
    version 0.5

DESCRIPTION
    A perl module to interface Philips Hue devices. See http://meethue.com

    To use the examples in the examples folder, please configure the
    environment appropriately:

    export HUE_BRIDGE="http://192.168.1.123" =item export
    HUE_KEY="7c1590fb6089be2129260acb2df53372"

